data.description: SELLERS OFFERING $5k in CLOSING COSTS w/acceptable offer!  Imagine yourself in this popular WATERFRONT COMMUNITY of Harbor Cove by 2024!  This 4 bedroom home sits comfortably on .3 acre lot and features a huge fenced-in backyard, fire pit, 12 x 16 outbuilding, & large patio offering terrific outdoor living space!   The interior features nicely appointed kitchen updated in 2015 w/soft-close cabinetry, granite counters, stainless appliances (including refrigerator), smooth top stove, & island. Cozy wood burning fireplace in family room.  Engineered hardwood floors on most of main;  Laundry conveniently located on upper level - Washer & Dryer are NEW & convey!  Spacious primary bedroom has walk- in closet & huge tray ceiling.  Large bonus rm w/closet functions as 4th bedrm.  NEW AC 2020, NEW furnace 2021; NEW Rennai tankless hot water heater 2022;  The community offers a pool as well as lake access for paddle boards/kayaks.  Convenient to schools, restaurants, shopping, hospital & I-77!
